dataSources.Rd

Table of data sources used for parameters

dataSources

Format

A tibble with 5 columns and 8 rows:

description

Description of data source

parameter

Model parameter data source addresses

source

Issuing authority or body of the data source

scode

Source code

format

Format of the data available from the data source

link

URL for data source

dataSources
